N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4821.4 - Report when no games are played

State Regulations

When no games are held on any date when a license
authorizes them to be held, a report to that effect must be filed with the
clerk of the municipality and the commission. Notes
